WEBVTT

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.640
Did you just touch her?

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:31.000
Darn it.

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:32.920
The big boss showed up so fast.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:33.879
Stay calm.

00:01:33.879 --> 00:01:34.680
Think of something.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:36.200
Brother Zhantian!

00:01:36.599 --> 00:01:37.400
It's a misunderstanding!

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.599
We're on the same side!

00:01:39.239 --> 00:01:41.000
How do you know my name?

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:42.480
Qingqiu, of course.

00:01:42.480 --> 00:01:43.719
She talks about you all the time.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:44.719
She said...

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:45.719
there's this security guard...

00:01:46.239 --> 00:01:47.480
who is incredibly handsome...

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:48.760
and...

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:49.879
has a great sense of justice.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.040
Is that so?

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:57.680
He smiled.

00:01:57.879 --> 00:01:58.680
Good.

00:01:58.799 --> 00:01:59.599
Press the advantage.

00:01:59.799 --> 00:02:00.599
Yeah.

00:02:01.239 --> 00:02:02.480
And she also said...

00:02:02.599 --> 00:02:03.840
that whenever she's in danger,

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:04.400
this guy always...

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:05.239
shows up immediately.

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:06.239
And he has this commanding aura.

00:02:06.239 --> 00:02:07.439
When those small fries see him,

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:08.039
they can't wait to...

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:08.919
kneel and kowtow to him.

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:10.599
That must be you, right?

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:12.439
That's true.

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:14.439
Then...

00:02:25.439 --> 00:02:27.039
Thank you, Brother Zhantian,

00:02:27.039 --> 00:02:28.000
for lifting your foot.

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:29.719
But just now, I was outside

00:02:29.719 --> 00:02:31.039
and heard a commotion inside.

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:32.039
What's going on?

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:35.039
I was just talking to Qingqiu

00:02:35.039 --> 00:02:35.719
about

00:02:35.719 --> 00:02:37.080
canceling the engagement.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.159
Canceling?

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.439
You'd do such a good deed?

00:02:40.719 --> 00:02:42.199
Actually, I've always felt

00:02:42.439 --> 00:02:43.719
that my looks

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:44.800
and charm

00:02:45.039 --> 00:02:46.039
aren't good enough for Qingqiu.

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:48.800
But I think Brother Zhantian is a perfect match!

00:02:49.439 --> 00:02:50.120
Brother Zhantian,

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.520
your domineering aura

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.240
matches Qingqiu perfectly.

00:02:54.439 --> 00:02:54.919
However,

00:02:54.919 --> 00:02:56.560
between Qingqiu and me,

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:58.439
whoever proposes to cancel the engagement

00:02:58.520 --> 00:03:00.120
will damage their family's honor.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.360
So I'd like to ask Brother Zhantian

00:03:01.439 --> 00:03:02.840
to lend me a hand.

00:03:06.039 --> 00:03:06.560
I'm really

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:07.840
such a genius.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:09.439
Not only can I break away from the original plotline,

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:10.479
but I can also make Gu Zhantian

00:03:10.479 --> 00:03:11.639
owe me a favor.

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:15.479
You'd better not play tricks on me.

00:03:15.759 --> 00:03:16.560
Don't worry.

00:03:17.039 --> 00:03:18.840
Everything is under control.

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:20.080
Ladies

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:20.840
and gentlemen,

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:23.280
and all the distinguished guests and friends here,

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:24.520
welcome to

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:25.479
Mr. Lu Chengwen

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:27.000
and Miss Leng Qingqiu's

00:03:27.199 --> 00:03:28.479
engagement ceremony!

00:03:29.199 --> 00:03:30.039
Great!

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.199
Good!

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.319
Qingqiu,

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.919
I know you don't want to get married either.

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:34.879
It's fine.

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:35.680
Don't worry.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:37.039
I've arranged everything.

00:03:38.199 --> 00:03:40.080
Gu Zhantian will come to crash the party later.

00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:41.439
I'll take the opportunity to let Leng Qingqiu

00:03:41.439 --> 00:03:42.319
be his spare tire.

00:03:42.599 --> 00:03:44.080
Out of sight, out of mind.

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:45.199
Being a spare tire again?

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:46.680
Disgusting.

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:47.599
Lu Chengwen,

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:48.639
for offending me,

00:03:48.639 --> 00:03:50.439
you're going to suffer a bit.

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:51.639
Wait.

00:03:54.639 --> 00:03:55.639
Who is this?

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.400
Is he here to cause trouble?

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:03.280
What nonsense is he spouting?

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:05.199
I object!

00:04:05.639 --> 00:04:06.400
Good job!

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.159
As expected of the male lead.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.159
Perfect timing.

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:08.919
Who is it?

00:04:08.919 --> 00:04:09.439
Who's this?

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:10.039
I don't know.

00:04:10.039 --> 00:04:10.840
A lousy security guard?

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:12.000
Why is he causing trouble?

00:04:12.199 --> 00:04:13.400
Is he here to steal the bride?

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.319
Who is this guy?

00:04:15.919 --> 00:04:16.720
Miss Leng,

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:18.480
I know you are

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:20.079
being forced to marry Lu Chengwen.

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:21.399
But don't worry.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:22.639
With me here,

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:23.920
no one will force you

00:04:23.920 --> 00:04:25.800
to do anything you don't want to do.

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:31.319
How insolent!

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:32.560
Daring to disturb the young master's wedding?

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:32.959
I think you have

00:04:32.959 --> 00:04:33.639
a death wish!

00:04:44.959 --> 00:04:45.759
You've suffered.

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:46.639
Gangzi.

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:47.199
Later,

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:48.399
I'll give you a sports car.

00:04:52.839 --> 00:04:54.000
That was a brutal beating.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:54.639
Seriously.

00:04:54.839 --> 00:04:55.639
Qingqiu,

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:58.879
let's go home.

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:06.600
Gu Zhantian,

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:07.319
you are

00:05:07.319 --> 00:05:08.319
fired.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.199
Huh?

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:10.279
Wait.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:15.360
A scumbag like you

00:05:15.399 --> 00:05:16.839
wants to control me?

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:17.639
Hmph.

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.319
Today is the big day

00:05:20.319 --> 00:05:21.399
of my engagement.

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:24.040
You're just a lowly security guard.

00:05:24.519 --> 00:05:26.240
Who allowed you to cause trouble here?

00:05:26.879 --> 00:05:27.319
Exactly.

00:05:27.319 --> 00:05:28.120
Yeah.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:31.839
He's the one causing trouble.

00:05:32.279 --> 00:05:33.079
Coming here to cause trouble.

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:34.480
What's going on?

00:05:39.279 --> 00:05:40.040
Seeing you looking like

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.720
a stray dog,

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:43.480
why do I feel an

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:45.279
uncontrollable sense of satisfaction?

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:50.040
Qingqiu,

00:05:51.079 --> 00:05:53.040
did he threaten you to do this?

00:05:53.399 --> 00:05:55.399
No one can threaten me, Leng Qingqiu.

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:57.399
Lu Chengwen,

00:05:57.639 --> 00:05:58.600
let's get engaged.

00:05:59.480 --> 00:05:59.800
Ah?

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.279
I'm willing to be with you.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.199
Young Miss,

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:10.639
you're trying to get me killed, aren't you?

00:06:23.519 --> 00:06:24.800
What's wrong with me?

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:27.399
I've never felt so comfortable before.

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:28.800
Lu Chengwen,

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:30.000
you really are a

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.079
treasure.

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:34.040
I don't agree to the engagement!

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:38.199
Calm down.

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:39.000
Think of a way.

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.439
I can't let her drag me into this.

00:06:41.079 --> 00:06:42.040
I think,

00:06:42.079 --> 00:06:43.480
I shouldn't give up an entire forest

00:06:43.480 --> 00:06:44.800
just for one flower.

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:45.519
Right?

00:06:45.519 --> 00:06:46.360
Everyone here,

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:47.040
uncles and aunts,

00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:48.279
your daughters,

00:06:48.319 --> 00:06:49.399
relatives, or whatever,

00:06:49.399 --> 00:06:49.959
How can he say that?

00:06:49.959 --> 00:06:50.879
if there are pretty ones,

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:51.879
with good figures,

00:06:51.879 --> 00:06:53.199
feel free to introduce them to me.

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:55.079
I can have a deep exchange with them.

00:06:55.079 --> 00:06:55.839
Hahaha.

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:56.920
How can this guy be like this?

00:06:57.920 --> 00:06:58.800
This is too much.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.240
How can they still get married?

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:01.040
Leng Qingqiu,

00:07:01.079 --> 00:07:02.519
someone who cares about face as much as you,

00:07:02.639 --> 00:07:03.800
couldn't possibly tolerate this, right?

00:07:04.839 --> 00:07:06.800
He doesn't even know I've heard all of his Mind voice.

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:07.920
Son of a bitch,

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:09.079
still acting here.

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:09.920
Qingqiu,

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.800
did you hear what this guy is saying?

00:07:12.399 --> 00:07:13.639
He's just a scumbag.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:15.199
As long as you nod,

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:16.360
I can make this guy

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:17.680
disappear forever.

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:19.000
Wow.

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:19.720
Gu Zhantian,

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:20.800
burning bridges.

00:07:20.879 --> 00:07:22.240
You're just using me as a stepping stone.

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:23.639
Gu Zhantian,

00:07:23.839 --> 00:07:25.319
I don't want to see you right now.

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:26.680
Be sensible

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.800
and leave quickly.

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:29.519
Qingqiu...

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:30.399
Get lost!

00:07:40.279 --> 00:07:41.199
Darn it, darn it.

00:07:41.319 --> 00:07:42.680
He's definitely holding a grudge now.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.399
But at least I wasn't beaten to death.

00:07:45.279 --> 00:07:46.079
Lu Chengwen.

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:47.240
Shall we continue?

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:48.439
I'll listen to whatever you say.

00:07:51.439 --> 00:07:52.079
Ah.

00:07:53.279 --> 00:07:54.399
Marriage is a big deal.

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:55.199
As for you,

00:07:55.199 --> 00:07:56.480
go back and think it over.

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.040
Ah.

00:07:57.519 --> 00:07:58.399
Let's talk another day.

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:01.800
This is really too much.

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:03.240
It's so humiliating.

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:07.800
Ah.

00:08:13.639 --> 00:08:14.240
Ah.

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:16.920
Congratulations.

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:18.000
After so many tries,

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.240
you finally passed the first level.

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:23.639
I passed?

00:08:24.439 --> 00:08:27.720
Hahaha!

00:08:27.879 --> 00:08:28.680
As expected,

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.279
I knew it.

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:32.080
Laying low is the way to go.

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:33.799
Sigh.

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:36.399
However,

00:08:36.679 --> 00:08:37.720
Leng Qingqiu...

00:08:37.720 --> 00:08:39.240
Why didn't she follow the plotline

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.320
and leave with Gu Zhantian?

00:08:40.639 --> 00:08:41.639
I'm also confused.

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:43.200
But I don't have a clue yet.

00:08:43.879 --> 00:08:44.679
By the way,

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.840
as a reward for passing the first level,

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:49.240
this King Wen's Medical Tome

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:50.399
is now passed on to you.

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:51.679
It cures all diseases.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:53.759
Ah.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:55.559
Hmm.

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:58.519
What do you mean it cures all diseases?

00:08:58.799 --> 00:08:59.279
It's just

00:08:59.279 --> 00:09:00.679
a setting in the novel, right?

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.200
Did you forget what I told you?

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.240
The rewards from here

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.240
can all be brought back

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:05.519
to your world.

00:09:07.879 --> 00:09:08.679
Right.

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:10.639
I've never passed a level before.

00:09:10.799 --> 00:09:11.360
So,

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:13.000
I almost forgot about this.

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:13.799
Oh my.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:14.639
Number Six.

00:09:14.879 --> 00:09:15.519
Ah.

00:09:15.519 --> 00:09:16.320
No,

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:17.399
Sister Six.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:18.799
I forgot.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.840
Then you must never forget

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.440
who you are

00:09:23.639 --> 00:09:24.639
and what you are doing.

00:09:25.039 --> 00:09:26.519
You must keep your will to live.

00:09:29.399 --> 00:09:31.240
How could I forget who I am?

00:09:32.639 --> 00:09:33.799
I am

00:09:33.799 --> 00:09:35.279
someone who doesn't belong to this world.

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:36.480
In my world,

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.240
I have no money.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.799
I know you're in there!

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.600
Pay your rent in full right now,

00:09:41.639 --> 00:09:42.720
or get the hell out!

00:09:42.879 --> 00:09:44.039
Don't just squat here!

00:09:47.399 --> 00:09:48.440
I have no girlfriend.

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:51.639
What are you looking at?

00:09:51.919 --> 00:09:52.720
Disgusting.

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:01.519
And maybe,

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:02.840
I have no future either.

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.879
I told you not to watch shows while driving!

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:05.600
Is he dead?

00:10:05.679 --> 00:10:06.320
Let's call the police.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:06.720
He's not dead.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:07.279
No one is watching.

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:08.120
Let's get out of here.

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:10.080
But I can't die.

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:12.240
I must survive.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:14.360
Because...

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:15.799
Ma'am,

00:10:15.799 --> 00:10:17.039
didn't your son come today?

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:18.039
He should be here

00:10:18.039 --> 00:10:19.320
in a little while.

00:10:19.639 --> 00:10:21.080
He's very filial.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.600
Maybe today

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:24.000
he's a bit busy with work.

00:10:27.799 --> 00:10:29.399
Being defeated by me, Gu Zhantian,

00:10:30.039 --> 00:10:31.120
is your honor.

00:10:32.440 --> 00:10:33.080
Ah.

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:34.519
Why?

00:10:34.519 --> 00:10:36.240
Why am I the one being defeated?

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:37.720
I can't accept this.

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:39.440
I don't want to fall.

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:42.320
Is that so?

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:44.519
I can help you with that.

00:10:50.919 --> 00:10:51.720
However,

00:10:52.440 --> 00:10:54.120
you have to make a deal with me.

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:07.279
Ah.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:19.120
Lu Chengwen.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:21.240
Before we complete our deal,

00:11:21.840 --> 00:11:23.440
you absolutely cannot die.

00:11:23.799 --> 00:11:24.600
Don't worry.

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:27.240
More than anyone else,

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.120
I want to live.

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.440
Good luck,

00:11:29.679 --> 00:11:30.600
cutie.

00:11:37.279 --> 00:11:37.919
Ah!

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:40.679
Why did the timeline jump again?

00:11:41.039 --> 00:11:42.039
Where am I?

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:44.159
Isn't this one of Haicheng's major families,

00:11:44.159 --> 00:11:45.200
the Chen Family?

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:47.240
Young Master Lu,

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:48.240
Old Master Chen is awake.

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.879
But he doesn't really want to see you.

00:11:49.879 --> 00:11:50.519
Ah?

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:51.240
Wh-

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:52.519
Why doesn't he want to see me?

00:11:52.919 --> 00:11:53.799
Old Master Chen used to

00:11:53.799 --> 00:11:55.600
treat you like his own grandson.

00:11:55.799 --> 00:11:57.360
But last month, you set a trap

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:59.120
and scammed the Chen Family out of billions.

00:11:59.279 --> 00:12:00.240
So him not wanting to see you

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:01.480
is quite understandable, right?

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:02.759
Oh.

00:12:03.039 --> 00:12:04.240
U-Understandable.

00:12:04.919 --> 00:12:05.799
Th-Then,

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:07.000
I'll leave you to it.

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:08.200
I'll just leave the gift

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:08.840
and go.

00:12:08.840 --> 00:12:09.480
Mhm.

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:13.799
This character of mine

00:12:13.799 --> 00:12:15.240
really was a scumbag in the past.

00:12:21.279 --> 00:12:21.919
Well, well.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:24.240
Isn't this the one who just scammed Old Master Chen,

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:25.440
Young Master Lu?

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.000
You still have the nerve to come here.

00:12:27.039 --> 00:12:28.480
Such thick skin.

00:12:29.039 --> 00:12:29.840
Not good.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.799
Which of Gu Zhantian's spare tires is this,

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:32.919
coming to harm me now?